spec_data.Name: nodejs-passport-strategy
spec_data.Description:
This module exports an abstract Strategy class that is intended to be
subclassed when implementing concrete authentication strategies. Once
implemented, such strategies can be used by applications that utilize
Passport middleware for authentication.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:44:44 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: An abstract class implementing Passport's strategy API
